        searchbarStr = decHtml(searchbarStr);

        window.HEADER_DATA['sc-header-config']['searchbar'] = JSON.parse(searchbarStr);

            });

            initHeader();
        }
    });

seajs.iuse("//i.alicdn.com/sc-list/gallery/location/location.js")(function(Location){
    var location = null

    try {
	    location = new Location({
	      element: '[data-content="location"]',
	      isExportCountry: false,
	    });	
    } catch (e) {
    	console.log('error when trying to create Location Instance', e)
    	location = null;
    }

    if (!location) {
    	return ;
    }

					location.setModel(location.getData("location"), location.getI18n(), location.getStatic(0));
			location.renderLocation();
			location.controller();
		
					var exportCountry = new Location({
				element: '[data-content="export-country"]',
				isExportCountry: true,
			})
			exportCountry.setModel(exportCountry.getData("exportCountry"), exportCountry.getI18n(), exportCountry.getStatic(0));
			exportCountry.renderLocation();
			exportCountry.controller();
		  })
</script>

    (function(){
        function attachEvent(el, t, h) {
            if (el.addEventListener) {
                el.addEventListener(t, h, false);
            } else if (el.attachEvent) {
                el.attachEvent('on' + t, h);
            }
        }
